Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:50.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたそのものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:50.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So now that you & I
